  <description>Desert Mirage is a 3D third-person mystery-adventure game with investigation and a choices matter narrative.</description>

  <!-- Choose between a single block: -->
  <history>
    Using a compass that does not point north, the adventure begins upon arrival in the city of Lagoinhas, 
    where you must explore the region and discover what happened to your sister in the middle of a desert.
    <br>
    Bia find a strange compass and sets out to uncover the truth in a dark, mysterious town. By talking to locals, 
    she gathers clues to decide her path. Guided by the mysterious compass, she explores a desert of oasis, 
    solving puzzles across diverse environments, until she discovers the truth.
    In the heart of the desert, every choice is a crossroads, shaping your journey and deciding the future of the ones you love.
  </history>

